Bionomics.
The specimens were collected in subtropical broadleaved forest (with big tree ferns) with bamboo, by sifting of pile of rotting, mouldy bamboo shoots near a small creek ([T 
167
]), and by sifting bark, humus and various debris (some old mushrooms) around bases of old, dead standing trees in a forest clearing ([T 
20
]).
